Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.81,0:23:23.58,EDCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2.5}起舞 躍動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.58,0:23:25.30,EDCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2.5}摸摸 蹭蹭 ahaha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:27.07,EDCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2.5}好癢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.07,0:23:28.84,EDCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2.5}毛茸茸 鬆拋拋 ahaha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.84,0:23:30.61,EDCHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2.5}起舞 躍動
